OL,6,FAn armed attacker who stabbed a bus
OL,7,Fdriver in east London was tracked down
OL,8,Fand jailed with the help of facial
OL,9,Frecognition technology.
OL,11,FBradley Peek seriously injured the
OL,12,Fdriver who was left with damaged
OL,13,Fheart, fractures to seven ribs and a
OL,14,Fpunctured lung.
OL,16,FHe launched his savage attack after
OL,17,Fintervening in an argument between the
OL,18,Fdriver and someone he knew.
