OL,6,FWithin hours of the stabbing
OL,7,Fdetectives identified Peek using CCTV
OL,8,Fimages and facial recognition tech.
OL,10,FHe was jailed for five years following
OL,11,Fthe attack on Commercial Road in Tower
OL,12,FHamlets.
OL,14,FHave you heard our new podcast Talking
OL,15,FPolitics? Every week Tom, Robert and
OL,16,FAnushka dig into the biggest issues
OL,17,Fdominating the political agenda...
