OL,4,Cheart tracked down with facial tech
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Jonathan Potter,
OL,7,Fwho led the investigation, said: "This
OL,8,Fwas a senseless attack and a huge team
OL,9,Feffort from officers across the Met to
OL,10,Fsecure justice for the victim.
OL,12,F"The use of facial recognition
OL,13,Ftechnology and CCTV footage allowed
OL,14,Fofficers to quickly identify and
OL,15,Flocate Peek. I would also like to
OL,16,Fthank colleagues from the Royal London
OL,17,FHospital who performed an emergency
OL,18,Foperation which ultimately saved the
OL,19,Fvictim's life.
