OL,6,F"Facial recognition technology is used
OL,7,Fto be more precise in how we tackle
OL,8,Fcrime and identify wanted offenders.
OL,9,FIt assists the Met in targeting people
OL,10,Fwho are responsible for causing
OL,11,Fserious violence."
OL,13,FSiwan Hayward, Director of Security,
OL,14,FPolicing and Enforcement at TfL,
OL,15,Fadded: "This was an appalling act of
OL,16,Fviolence against our colleague who was
OL,17,Fjust trying to do their job.
