OL,6,F"Our staff have the right to do their
OL,7,Fjob without fear or intimidation and
OL,8,Fwe do not tolerate any violence,
OL,9,Faggression or threatening behaviour
OL,10,Ftowards them.
OL,12,F"We will always work with the police
OL,13,Fto push for the strongest sentences
OL,14,Fpossible for offenders, and we're
OL,15,Fpleased that the offender has been
OL,16,Fbrought to justice."
